(40, 25, 21, 43, 12, 26, 26, 'thou good and faithful servant', 'Service and Reward', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of serving and being rewarded. In Matthew, the faithful servant is honored with greater responsibility, while in John, serving Jesus leads to honor from the Father.', 'theme', 0.5449999999999999, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 25, 21, 55, 2, 12, 12, 'thou good and faithful servant', 'Faithfulness and Reigning', 'Both passages emphasize the reward for faithfulness. In Matthew, the faithful servant is promised rulership, while in 2 Timothy, suffering for Christ leads to reigning with Him.', 'theme', 0.45399999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
